Class Food

  • java.lang.Object
    • Assignment.Food
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Item, PromoSet
    public abstract class Food
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an abstract class that serves as a Parent class for any kind of food that needs to be listed on the menu.
